"Hey!" Prowl yells, spinning around as Iron Raptor jumps past him, 
smashing into the door. He runs toward the door, stopping a few 
inches from it.

"Love, please calm down, if you co out there and start tearing bots 
apart, you won't last long!

> 
> * She kept her eyes on him at all times, never taking them from 
him...or 
> blinking either.
> If he suddenly moved towards her, she wanted to see it.

doubtful

lose what

saying, 
> almost as if she could actually consider doing what he asked...but 
she knew 
> she couldn't.
> 
> Though, she knew that soon she would be just as mean as before, and 
that she 
> somehow had to get out of there...NOW!
> Her eyes shifting from Prowl and locking on the door behind him, 
moving

> Suddenly, without warning she suddenly heaved her muscles and 
whisked by
